snippet.title: GINGER CHICKEN | 500 Chicken Legs With Ginger | Traditional Ginger Chicken Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook ginger chicken recipe by using 500 chicken legs and a huge amount of ginger. We first cut and fried the ginger separately. Then, we marinate the chicken in curd and lemon juice. Finally, we cook them all together.

The taste is delicious!

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Get Ready For Town Hall 16! Clash of Clans New Update
snippet.description:
Town Hall 16‚Äôs nature theme is easy to see with its tree-influenced design. Even Town Hall 16‚Äôs Giga Inferno beam is like a magnified solar blast from the sun.¬†


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong : The New Empire | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in theaters 2024

The epic battle continues!  Legendary Pictures‚Äô cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence‚Äîand our own. ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire‚Äù delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard.  The film stars Rebecca Hall (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù The Night House‚Äù), Brian Tyree Henry (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), Dan Stevens (‚ÄúGaslit,‚Äù ‚ÄúLegion,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), Kaylee Hottle (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù), Alex Ferns (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúWrath of Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúChernobyl‚Äù) and Fala Chen (‚ÄúIrma Vep,‚Äù ‚ÄúShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù the ‚ÄúPirates of the Caribbean‚Äù series) and Simon Barrett (‚ÄúYou‚Äôre Next‚Äù) and Jeremy Slater (‚ÄúMoon Knight‚Äù), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd..  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni and Brian Rogers.  The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira. 

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúWorld War Z‚Äù), production designer Tom Hammock (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúX,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Guest‚Äù), editor Josh Schaeffer (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMolly‚Äôs Game‚Äù), costume designer Emily Seresin (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop of the Lake‚Äù).  The composers are Tom Holkenborg (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSonic the Hedgehog‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.‚Äù  It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on April 12, 2024 and beginning 10 April 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.

snippet.title: Dating Mausi Ki Student - Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi (Crowd Work Video)
snippet.description:
Hello Doston,

Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy crowd work video:
Dating Mausi Ki Student which was recorded in my comedy show called BEST OF GUPTAJI.

This is a New Stand Up Comedy video which we have recorded in October at The Comedy Theatre, Gurgoan

Hope you enjoy this latest comedy video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai and Genuinely, I am presenting my new show with an old name Best of GuptaJi which I am starting to tour now.
Why Best of GuptaJi? because I want all the content in my show to be the best content from my side. So if you have seen my videos on chai, maggi, hotel, airport, tinder, starbucks etc, it was a part of Best of GuptaJi only so am trying to give you new content but with that level only.

If you want to come for the Best of GuptaJi tour, here is the ticket link : https://linktr.ee/appurvgupta

Book Now as we have limited seats in every city.

--------------------------------------------------------
Tappu and his friends play badminton near his scooter i.e. Sakharam. Unfortunately, Goli falls over Sakharam. Bhide gets angry at Tapu Sena for playing badminton near Sakhram. snippet.title: New Update - Town Hall 16 in Clash of Clans!
snippet.description:
TH16 Update Sneak Peek for Clash of Clans! Judo Sloth Gaming shares Town Hall 16 Gameplay as well as information on New Troop and Defense Levels coming in the update. There are numerous building upgrades shared alongside Balance Changes, Cost Reductions and the ability to finally attack your own base! This is only Sneak Peek 1 for the CoC December Update so be sure to subscribe for more Town Hall 16 content. The exact TH16 release date is not confirmed yet but it is typically shortly after sneak peeks and will be after Hammer Jam is finished. Clash On!

snippet.description:

As he explains, there are times when you have to choose between the right thing to do and the fun thing to do. In Mannpasand, Zakir firmly chooses fun.

snippet.title: Bobby Deol Interview | ‚ÄòAlways knew Animal will work‚Äô | Ranbir Kapoor | Gadar 2 | Dharmendra
snippet.description:
In a candid chat with Pinkvilla, Bobby Deol opens up about the historic success of Animal, the bond with Ranbir Kapoor on the sets, and the vision of director Sandeep Reddy Vanga. The actor decodes his iconic entry scene and speaks from his heart about the success tasted by brother Sunny Deol and father Dharmendra in 2023 with Gadar 2 and Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani. Bobby also gives an update on Soldier 2, Animal 2 and Apne 2 and explains what would it take for him to come on board a comedy. Watch Video.

snippet.title: 99 Details From the GTA 6 Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss our GTA 6 trailer breakdown! The GTA 6 trailer is finally here and we've looked over the entire footage and uncovered 99 hidden and hard to find details littered throughout our first look at GTA VI.

There are lots of cool new things to pick out from this brand new Grand Theft Auto 6 trailer from Rockstar Games, and in our GTA 6 trailer deep dive, we examine clues about GTA 6 map locations, hints about the GTA 6 world, glimpses of what might happen in the GTA 6 story, references to GTA Vice City, and more.

The GTA 6 release date is 2025 on PS5 and Xbox Series X/S.

Credit to tachyon_v for the map creation 

For more on Grand Theft Auto VI, check out our GTA 6 trailer reaction video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuMSEkVqC9k

#GTA6 #GTA #Gaming

Bhide's "Suvichaar" or thought of the day states that anger, pain, and agony are a waste of energy and time so people should avoid engaging themselves in these. snippet.description:
CID cast members Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava, Tanya Abrol, and Ansha Sayed gathered at the crematorium to pay their respects to the late actor Dinesh Phadnis, who passed away last night. His last rites took place at Daulat Nagar crematorium in Borivali around 10:30-11 am. The actor, who battled for his life, succumbed around 12 am after being admitted to Tunga Hospital in Mumbai. ETimes TV got to speak with the actors, who shared their fond memories.
